MANIFEST

# PyInstaller
#  Usually these files are written by a python script, and contain the binery number of the python-script-encoded-with-zlib.
#  Extracting the inside of them reveals the python-script-with-zlib-metadata-and-without-python-metadata.
#  The metadata is needed for pyinstaller to be able to extract the script.
*.manifest
*.spec

# Installer logs
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

